      "message": "[Critical] Line 128: `bodyOverwrite` from plugin data is rendered as the message body without preserving the original body in the edit history path. For edited messages, `previousBodies` now stores the overwritten text when an edition contains `bodyOverwrite`, so the UI may expose plugin-generated text as if it were the user\u0027s authored content. Keep plugin display overrides separate from canonical message bodies and only use the original body for editing/history/audit data.\n```suggestion\nconst auto originalBody \u003d edition.value(\"body\");\npreviousBodies.append(Body {edition.value(\"id\"), originalBody, QString(edition.value(\"timestamp\")).toInt()});\n```",
